---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy | Tec Electrical Services Ltd"
	description="How Tec Electrical Services Ltd collects, uses, and protects personal information submitted through this website."
>
	<SiteHeader />

	<main class="legal-page">
		<section class="legal-intro" aria-labelledby="privacy-page-title">
			<div class="legal-wrap">
				<p class="legal-eyebrow">Legal</p>
				<h1 id="privacy-page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="legal-lead">How we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="legal-content" aria-labelledby="privacy-content-heading">
			<div class="legal-wrap">
				<article class="legal-card">
					<h2 id="privacy-content-heading">Tec Electrical Services Ltd Privacy Policy</h2>
					<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 8 May 2026</p>

					<p>
						This Privacy Policy explains how Tec Electrical Services Ltd collects and uses personal data when you contact us
						through this website, by phone, or by email.
					</p>

					<h3>1. Who we are</h3>
					<p>
						Tec Electrical Services Ltd is the data controller for the personal information we collect in relation to
						enquiries, quotations, and service delivery.
					</p>

					<h3>2. What information we collect</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Name and contact details (phone number, email address, postcode, address where provided)</li>
						<li>Details about your enquiry, project requirements, and preferred appointment times</li>
						<li>Any information you choose to include in messages or attachments</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>3. How we use your information</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>To respond to enquiries and provide quotations</li>
						<li>To plan, deliver, and support electrical works</li>
						<li>To maintain service records and communicate project updates</li>
						<li>To meet legal, regulatory, and insurance requirements</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>4. Lawful basis for processing</h3>
					<p>We process personal data under one or more of the following lawful bases:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Consent (for enquiry submissions where you opt in)</li>
						<li>Contract (to provide requested services)</li>
						<li>Legitimate interests (to run and improve our business operations)</li>
						<li>Legal obligation (where compliance is required)</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>5. Data sharing</h3>
					<p>
						We only share personal information where necessary, for example with trusted suppliers, subcontractors, or
						service providers supporting quotation, scheduling, communication, and compliance processes.
					</p>

					<h3>6. Data retention</h3>
					<p>
						We keep personal data only for as long as necessary for enquiry handling, service delivery, record keeping, and
						legal obligations.
					</p>

					<h3>7. Your rights</h3>
					<p>Subject to applicable law, you may have the right to:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
						<li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
						<li>Request deletion or restriction of processing</li>
						<li>Object to certain processing activities</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>8. Contact us about privacy</h3>
					<p>
						If you have any privacy-related queries, please contact us at
						<a href="mailto:hello@tecservicesltd.com">hello@tecservicesltd.com</a>.
					</p>

					<p class="legal-note">
						Please also review our <a href="/terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>.
					</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.legal-page {
		background: #f8fafc;
	}

	.legal-content {
		padding: 1.1rem var(--site-content-padding) 4rem;
	}

	.legal-wrap {
		max-width: 980px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.legal-intro {
		padding: 2.4rem var(--site-content-padding) 0.6rem;
	}

	.legal-eyebrow {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: #3567ab;
	}

	.legal-intro h1 {
		margin: 0.52rem 0 0.35rem;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.65rem);
		line-height: 1.1;
		color: #0f172a;
	}

	.legal-lead {
		margin: 0;
		color: #64748b;
		font-size: 0.98rem;
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.legal-card {
		background: #fff;
		border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
		border-radius: 0.95rem;
		padding: 1.3rem 1.25rem;
		box-shadow: 0 14px 30px -24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.34);
	}

	.legal-card h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.2vw, 1.9rem);
		color: #0f172a;
	}

	.legal-card h3 {
		margin: 1.1rem 0 0.35rem;
		font-size: 1.02rem;
		color: #1e293b;
	}

	.legal-card p,
	.legal-card li {
		font-size: 0.96rem;
		line-height: 1.62;
		color: #475569;
	}

	.legal-card ul {
		margin: 0.45rem 0 0;
		padding-left: 1.1rem;
	}

	.legal-card a {
		color: #0f4ac4;
		text-decoration: underline;
		text-underline-offset: 0.12em;
	}

	.legal-note {
		margin-top: 1.4rem;
		padding-top: 0.95rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
	}
</style>
